        <title>CHANGE OIL LAMP</title>
        <para>The Change Oil Lamp is cycled momentarily on at every key on cycle as part of a visual bulb check. It is
            mounted in the instrument cluster and receives 12 volt power from the cluster. The lamp is illuminated when
            the ECM completes the path to ground. Refer to circuit diagram
            <emph type="BOLD">Figure
                <hotlnk document="e190_170.xml" xrefid="f1901731">3.35</hotlnk>
            </emph>
            .
        </para>
